(Directed by Liu Xue Song)

3
00:01:34,480 --> 00:01:37,159
(Episode 33)

4
00:01:44,439 --> 00:01:45,439
(Hou Jue)

5
00:02:02,280 --> 00:02:03,719
Hello, Mr. Hou Junior.

6
00:02:04,359 --> 00:02:05,680
I'm not Mr. Hou Junior now.

7
00:02:05,680 --> 00:02:07,000
I'm just an employee now.

8
00:02:07,799 --> 00:02:09,090
What have you been up to?

9
00:02:09,090 --> 00:02:10,199
Have you left the company?

10
00:02:10,199 --> 00:02:11,370
I'm sorry.

11
00:02:11,599 --> 00:02:14,479
If you're here to persuade me on behalf of Hou Zhi Rong,

12
00:02:14,680 --> 00:02:16,400
I don't think that's necessary.

13
00:02:16,759 --> 00:02:18,039
I don't have time for that.

14
00:02:18,960 --> 00:02:20,560
Don't you know I've moved out?

15
00:02:21,370 --> 00:02:23,120
I'm working at Hedgehog Factory now.

16
00:02:23,919 --> 00:02:25,199
It's quite nice here.

17
00:02:25,199 --> 00:02:26,960
They're working...

18
00:02:26,960 --> 00:02:28,400
on a proposal for the Ruiji Bid.

19
00:02:29,759 --> 00:02:31,810
That's great. Congratulations.

20
00:02:32,000 --> 00:02:33,530
Hurry and work on it then.

21
00:02:33,879 --> 00:02:35,159
Why are you still looking for me?

22
00:02:35,530 --> 00:02:38,400
I'm planning to go on a trip to clear my head now.

23
00:02:39,370 --> 00:02:40,759
You can go on a trip anytime.

24
00:02:41,319 --> 00:02:43,039
Are you not willing to help me?

25
00:02:43,199 --> 00:02:44,719
Hurry up. I'm waiting for you.

26
00:02:45,400 --> 00:02:46,840
I'll send you the address right away.

27
00:02:47,000 --> 00:02:48,120
I'm hanging up. Bye.

28
00:02:49,039 --> 00:02:50,599
But I'm already on the bus...

29
00:02:51,520 --> 00:02:53,280
Hello?

30
00:02:55,599 --> 00:02:59,120
Gosh. You're just like your dad.

31
00:03:00,000 --> 00:03:02,159
Doesn't it go like this?

32
00:03:11,319 --> 00:03:13,039
All right. Everyone, get off.

33
00:03:13,039 --> 00:03:14,039
Wake up.

34
00:03:15,439 --> 00:03:16,680
Come out one by one.

35
00:03:16,680 --> 00:03:17,759
Don't forget anything.

36
00:03:17,759 --> 00:03:18,879
All right, let's go.

37
00:03:20,960 --> 00:03:22,240
We're all here.

38
00:03:22,360 --> 00:03:23,599
Let's go to the front.

39
00:03:25,120 --> 00:03:27,120
Don't forget your belongings.

40
00:03:30,680 --> 00:03:32,319
All right. It's just up ahead.

41
00:03:58,599 --> 00:04:00,159
- You startled me. - You're finally here.

42
00:04:00,159 --> 00:04:01,560
I knew I could count on you.

43
00:04:01,560 --> 00:04:03,080
I knew you'd come.

44
00:04:03,639 --> 00:04:04,840
Is this Hedgehog Factory?

45
00:04:04,840 --> 00:04:06,080
How is it? Not bad, right?

46
00:04:06,400 --> 00:04:07,919
Now this is what you call a place...

47
00:04:07,919 --> 00:04:09,280
where designers can create.

48
00:04:09,560 --> 00:04:10,680
Sit here. I'll get you something to drink.

49
00:04:10,680 --> 00:04:11,680
Okay.

50
00:04:12,120 --> 00:04:13,280
What would you like to drink?

51
00:04:13,280 --> 00:04:14,400
Anything is fine.

52
00:04:15,560 --> 00:04:16,920
By the way, Hou Jue,

53
00:04:17,759 --> 00:04:21,050
you asked me to help you over the phone just now.

54
00:04:21,399 --> 00:04:22,800
If I'm not mistaken,

55
00:04:22,920 --> 00:04:24,050
do you mean...

56
00:04:24,319 --> 00:04:26,439
you want me to be your leader?

57
00:04:27,480 --> 00:04:28,759
You understood it...

58
00:04:30,480 --> 00:04:31,730
exactly right.

59
00:04:32,920 --> 00:04:34,199
It'll be a collaboration design.

60
00:04:34,199 --> 00:04:35,279
You're the boss.

61
00:04:35,839 --> 00:04:37,079
I'm the boss?

62
00:04:37,240 --> 00:04:40,170
But you've already worked here for quite some time.

63
00:04:40,170 --> 00:04:41,399
Why am I calling the shots?

64
00:04:42,279 --> 00:04:45,050
I'm having a mental block.

65
00:04:45,610 --> 00:04:47,439
I can't manage this alone, so I need your help.

66
00:04:47,439 --> 00:04:48,519
I'm telling you.

67
00:04:48,519 --> 00:04:49,759
Although Hedgehog Factory...

68
00:04:49,959 --> 00:04:51,730
is a small company,

69
00:04:52,170 --> 00:04:54,610
I believe we can help it...

70
00:04:54,610 --> 00:04:56,079
at least get noticed...

71
00:04:56,079 --> 00:04:57,439
and recognized in the market.

72
00:04:58,079 --> 00:04:59,680
There are many big companies now.

73
00:05:00,000 --> 00:05:01,240
Take my dad's company for example.

74
00:05:01,959 --> 00:05:03,730
Zhirong is indeed a very big company now,

75
00:05:03,730 --> 00:05:05,120
but they have weaknesses.

76
00:05:05,639 --> 00:05:07,730
They're under more pressure the bigger they get.

77
00:05:07,839 --> 00:05:10,279
Moreover, their thinking is too entrenched.

78
00:05:10,279 --> 00:05:12,639
They restrict their designers to only think inside the box.

79
00:05:12,639 --> 00:05:13,920
They can't innovate,

80
00:05:14,079 --> 00:05:16,199
make modifications, and create new things.

81
00:05:16,199 --> 00:05:17,439
We're different.

82
00:05:17,639 --> 00:05:19,759
Their era of entrenched thinking is already over.

83
00:05:20,050 --> 00:05:22,240
We are new blood.

84
00:05:22,360 --> 00:05:24,120
We represent the start of a new era.

85
00:05:24,120 --> 00:05:25,120
Isn't that right?

86
00:05:26,920 --> 00:05:28,040
I agree.

87
00:05:29,279 --> 00:05:30,399
Then stay.

88
00:05:30,519 --> 00:05:31,680
Tell me.

89
00:05:31,920 --> 00:05:34,120
What requests do you have for your salary? I'll ask for you.

90
00:05:34,920 --> 00:05:36,040
Hou Jue.

91
00:05:36,720 --> 00:05:38,680
I'm extremely petty...

92
00:05:39,000 --> 00:05:40,279
with people and companies that are also petty.

93
00:05:40,399 --> 00:05:42,560
But you're completely different. You're not that kind of person.

94
00:05:43,000 --> 00:05:45,120
So we don't need to discuss this kind of stuff.

95
00:05:45,480 --> 00:05:47,319
I already thought about it on my way here.

96
00:05:48,160 --> 00:05:49,720
No matter how much you're getting,

97
00:05:50,079 --> 00:05:51,360
I'll only take half of your salary.

98
00:05:51,360 --> 00:05:53,199
No more, no less.

99
00:05:53,920 --> 00:05:54,920
You have to agree.

100
00:05:54,920 --> 00:05:56,199
You have no other choice.

101
00:05:56,439 --> 00:05:58,279
All right, let's not talk about this.

102
00:05:58,439 --> 00:06:00,120
We're tight on time and we have an important mission.

103
00:06:00,120 --> 00:06:02,439
Hurry up and show me your design proposal.

104
00:06:04,480 --> 00:06:05,600
You're so reliable.

105
00:06:08,399 --> 00:06:10,079
Ms. Shi Yi, what are you eating for dinner?

106
00:06:10,480 --> 00:06:12,399
I don't know. I won't eat if I'm not hungry.

107
00:06:14,920 --> 00:06:16,399
Ms. Shi Yi, we're going back to our room then.

108
00:06:16,759 --> 00:06:18,040
- Okay, bye. - Bye, Ms. Shi Yi.

109
00:06:21,720 --> 00:06:22,839
Shi Yi.

110
00:06:23,480 --> 00:06:24,720
I'm glad I caught you.

111
00:06:25,160 --> 00:06:26,319
My villa has been cleaned.

112
00:06:26,319 --> 00:06:27,519
Your parents will be there soon.

113
00:06:27,519 --> 00:06:28,639
Let's go together.

114
00:06:29,560 --> 00:06:31,439
I already told them not to come.

115
00:06:32,000 --> 00:06:33,439
Are you stupid?

116
00:06:33,439 --> 00:06:34,600
Do you not want them to get back together?

117
00:06:36,439 --> 00:06:37,439
I do.

118
00:06:37,560 --> 00:06:39,199
But they still need to have feelings for each other.

119
00:06:39,600 --> 00:06:41,560
Otherwise, we can't force them to be together.

120
00:06:42,360 --> 00:06:43,680
You need to create opportunities...

121
00:06:43,680 --> 00:06:45,360
for feelings to develop.

122
00:06:45,720 --> 00:06:47,199
They're old now, so they're too embarrassed.

123
00:06:47,319 --> 00:06:48,680
We'll just have to take action for them then.

124
00:06:52,560 --> 00:06:53,879
Let's go, my bodyguard.

125
00:06:54,879 --> 00:06:56,120
I'll get changed.

126
00:06:56,120 --> 00:06:57,360
Wait for me downstairs.

127
00:06:57,920 --> 00:06:59,040
Go. Hurry up.

128
00:07:08,240 --> 00:07:09,800
All right, everyone.

129
00:07:11,160 --> 00:07:12,160
Let me introduce you.

130
00:07:12,160 --> 00:07:15,639
This is the famous designer,

131
00:07:15,639 --> 00:07:16,759
Bao Xiao Han.

132
00:07:16,959 --> 00:07:18,319
You guys know about Haicheng No. 8, right?

133
00:07:18,319 --> 00:07:19,439
He designed it.

134
00:07:20,399 --> 00:07:23,040
- Welcome. - Welcome.

135
00:07:23,279 --> 00:07:25,160
This is Mr. Xiao.

136
00:07:25,519 --> 00:07:27,360
- Hello, Mr. Xiao. - Just call me Zi Heng. Have a seat.

137
00:07:27,360 --> 00:07:28,439
No, that's not appropriate.

138
00:07:28,439 --> 00:07:30,160
Hurry up and sit. Don't be shy.

139
00:07:30,160 --> 00:07:31,399
Here, have some water.

140
00:07:32,040 --> 00:07:33,480
Chao Ren, you're here too.

141
00:07:33,480 --> 00:07:35,519
I came here a long time ago. You came late.

142
00:07:35,680 --> 00:07:37,199
Xiao Han, I've heard a lot about you.

143
00:07:37,199 --> 00:07:39,120
I didn't expect you to be so much more handsome in person.

144
00:07:40,600 --> 00:07:43,160
I saw your Haicheng No. 8 Project. It's awesome.

145
00:07:43,439 --> 00:07:45,000
I've seen a lot of your designs.

146
00:07:45,000 --> 00:07:46,279
You're my idol.

147
00:07:46,600 --> 00:07:47,920
You guys sound so fake.

148
00:07:47,920 --> 00:07:48,959
Is he your fake idol?

149
00:07:48,959 --> 00:07:50,959
In terms of looks, there's no way he's more handsome than me.

150
00:07:52,079 --> 00:07:54,639
Gosh. It's obvious he goes for a decadent look, right?

151
00:07:54,839 --> 00:07:56,079
All right.

152
00:07:56,079 --> 00:07:57,600
Don't praise me too much.

153
00:07:57,600 --> 00:07:58,600
I'm afraid I'll be arrogant.

154
00:07:59,079 --> 00:08:00,199
But...

155
00:08:00,319 --> 00:08:02,639
thank you so much for acknowledging me.

156
00:08:02,639 --> 00:08:03,639
I mean it.

157
00:08:05,480 --> 00:08:06,480
Hou Jue.

158
00:08:07,160 --> 00:08:10,040
This feeling is so great.

159
00:08:10,040 --> 00:08:11,199
It was worth coming here, right?

160
00:08:11,199 --> 00:08:13,480
I told you that you won't regret it if you work with me.

161
00:08:14,279 --> 00:08:15,519
Everyone knows him now, right?

162
00:08:15,680 --> 00:08:17,759
I won't introduce the rest to you now.

163
00:08:17,759 --> 00:08:19,439
You guys introduce yourselves at lunch later.

164
00:08:19,439 --> 00:08:20,439
If I introduce too many people to you at once,

165
00:08:20,439 --> 00:08:21,439
I'm afraid you won't be able to take it.

166
00:08:21,439 --> 00:08:22,439
Okay.

167
00:08:22,600 --> 00:08:24,439
Then on behalf of Hedgehog Factory,

168
00:08:24,560 --> 00:08:26,279
I formally extend a warm welcome...

169
00:08:26,279 --> 00:08:27,519
to Mr. Bao Xiao Han.

170
00:08:31,519 --> 00:08:32,519
You've played this game before.

171
00:08:33,000 --> 00:08:34,450
Let's welcome Bao Xiao Han again.

172
00:08:35,279 --> 00:08:36,919
- Welcome. - Thank you.

173
00:08:40,919 --> 00:08:42,039
It's this way. Come.

174
00:08:44,720 --> 00:08:46,120
The neighborhood is pretty nice, right?

175
00:08:46,399 --> 00:08:47,519
It's pretty good.

176
00:08:49,879 --> 00:08:51,159
- Is it in here? - Yes, it's this building.

177
00:08:53,090 --> 00:08:54,360
- Shi Yi, you're here. - Dad.

178
00:08:55,159 --> 00:08:56,399
What happened to your leg?

179
00:08:57,559 --> 00:08:59,450
I sprained my ankle. It's nothing serious.

180
00:08:59,759 --> 00:09:01,519
Lan Qi insisted on giving me a wheelchair.

181
00:09:02,360 --> 00:09:03,720
How is it? Are you getting used to it?

182
00:09:03,720 --> 00:09:05,330
Yes, it's easy to use.

183
00:09:05,330 --> 00:09:06,450
In a few days,

184
00:09:06,450 --> 00:09:08,279
I'll be able to play wheelchair basketball.

185
00:09:08,679 --> 00:09:10,210
Did you drink again?

186
00:09:11,120 --> 00:09:12,240
I drank too much.

187
00:09:13,210 --> 00:09:14,639
Luckily, your mom brought me home.

188
00:09:15,279 --> 00:09:16,399
Did my mom go to pick you up?

189
00:09:18,330 --> 00:09:19,450
You just started a new job.

190
00:09:19,450 --> 00:09:20,799
I didn't want to disturb you from your work,

191
00:09:20,799 --> 00:09:22,090
so I didn't tell you.

192
00:09:22,399 --> 00:09:23,559
You should've seen it yourself.

193
00:09:23,919 --> 00:09:27,000
Your dad was completely wasted that night.

194
00:09:27,120 --> 00:09:28,519
I even hurt my back.

195
00:09:28,840 --> 00:09:31,120
I have no idea how you used to carry him back home.

196
00:09:31,120 --> 00:09:32,559
I've already quit drinking.

197
00:09:32,559 --> 00:09:34,879
I didn't even drink a drop of alcohol this afternoon.

198
00:09:34,879 --> 00:09:36,000
You'd better quit.

199
00:09:36,759 --> 00:09:38,279
Enough of that. Let's go inside.

200
00:09:38,279 --> 00:09:39,399
Here, I'll push you.

201
00:09:40,090 --> 00:09:41,210
- I'll do it. - Come on, Mr. Wu.

202
00:09:41,840 --> 00:09:43,159
I don't really know how to push this.

203
00:09:45,600 --> 00:09:46,600
Shi Yi.

204
00:09:46,799 --> 00:09:48,759
Lan Qi took us around here.

205
00:09:48,759 --> 00:09:50,759
It's really nice here.

206
00:09:51,879 --> 00:09:54,600
It would be great if we could have a big dog here.

207
00:09:54,919 --> 00:09:56,919
You're even thinking of big dogs now. Gosh.

208
00:09:56,919 --> 00:09:58,039
Here, Mr. Wu and Ms. Zhang.

209
00:09:58,159 --> 00:10:00,399
I ordered food from the hotel,

210
00:10:00,399 --> 00:10:01,720
so it's going to be a while.

211
00:10:01,720 --> 00:10:03,000
- Let's eat some fruit first. - Okay. There's no rush.

212
00:10:04,090 --> 00:10:05,210
Here, Mr. Wu.

213
00:10:05,840 --> 00:10:08,360
Since we happen to have some time now,

214
00:10:08,360 --> 00:10:10,879
why don't we battle it out in the backyard?

215
00:10:10,879 --> 00:10:12,279
Chess? Let's go.

216
00:10:12,279 --> 00:10:13,399
Let's go.

217
00:10:14,090 --> 00:10:15,330
Let's go and play chess.

218
00:10:15,559 --> 00:10:18,519
Let the girls have their girl talk.

219
00:10:21,519 --> 00:10:22,759
Let's go.

220
00:10:23,799 --> 00:10:24,919
Be careful.

221
00:10:30,330 --> 00:10:31,450
Shi Yi.

222
00:10:34,039 --> 00:10:35,450
Hurry up. Come here.

223
00:10:37,519 --> 00:10:38,919
I'll bring it closer to you.

224
00:10:40,210 --> 00:10:41,330
How is it?

225
00:10:41,600 --> 00:10:42,600
What?

226
00:10:42,600 --> 00:10:43,960
Is work going well?

227
00:10:45,679 --> 00:10:46,679
Yes.

228
00:10:47,240 --> 00:10:48,600
It's going a little too well.

229
00:10:50,519 --> 00:10:51,759
What do you mean?

230
00:10:54,000 --> 00:10:56,240
It's such a well-paid and relaxing job.

231
00:10:57,240 --> 00:10:58,759
Lan Qi is also always taking care of me.

232
00:11:00,080 --> 00:11:01,320
He has given me so much.

233
00:11:02,000 --> 00:11:03,240
I feel anxious.

234
00:11:03,519 --> 00:11:05,120
What's there to be anxious about?

235
00:11:05,879 --> 00:11:07,919
This is a reward you deserve.

236
00:11:09,360 --> 00:11:10,480
Shi Yi.

237
00:11:11,759 --> 00:11:14,559
Having someone sincerely treat you well...

238
00:11:15,200 --> 00:11:16,440
is really hard to come by.

239
00:11:19,279 --> 00:11:20,279
I know.

240
00:11:21,240 --> 00:11:22,559
I know he's good to me.

241
00:11:22,759 --> 00:11:23,879
