485
00:27:19,839 --> 00:27:21,880
I'm coming over now. Don't go anywhere.

486
00:27:25,839 --> 00:27:26,839
Go on.

487
00:27:27,200 --> 00:27:28,319
We're here.

488
00:27:30,519 --> 00:27:31,640
You guys eat.

489
00:27:32,119 --> 00:27:33,119
Be careful.

490
00:27:35,920 --> 00:27:36,960
Mr. Xiao.

491
00:27:38,400 --> 00:27:40,920
I think my proposal is indeed a bit conservative.

492
00:27:41,680 --> 00:27:43,680
You have a bright future.

493
00:27:49,519 --> 00:27:50,720
Ma Yong.

494
00:27:52,359 --> 00:27:53,599
You're such a fool.

495
00:28:00,839 --> 00:28:03,160
We've been friends for so many years.

496
00:28:03,160 --> 00:28:05,559
You could've come to me if you ran into trouble.

497
00:28:05,559 --> 00:28:09,519
Why did you do such a stupid thing?

498
00:28:11,240 --> 00:28:14,200
I consider you my friend.

499
00:28:14,200 --> 00:28:16,799
Are you stupid?

500
00:28:30,039 --> 00:28:31,759
I have to find you.

501
00:28:32,279 --> 00:28:35,400
I have to personally ask you why you did this.

502
00:28:35,559 --> 00:28:38,240
Why did you do this to me?

503
00:28:38,799 --> 00:28:39,920
Why?

504
00:29:31,000 --> 00:29:32,000
Officers.

505
00:29:35,920 --> 00:29:37,039
Officers,

506
00:29:38,079 --> 00:29:39,680
I recognize that person.

507
00:29:55,920 --> 00:29:56,960
It was Ma Yong.

508
00:29:57,079 --> 00:29:58,400
Ma Yong was the one who harmed my dad.

509
00:29:58,920 --> 00:29:59,920
He ran off.

510
00:30:03,599 --> 00:30:05,240
(Ma Yong, The vice president of the company)

511
00:30:07,279 --> 00:30:08,319
(Hou Jue)

512
00:30:11,440 --> 00:30:13,480
Hello, where are you now?

513
00:30:13,960 --> 00:30:15,960
I'm going to Zhirong Construction to see my dad.

514
00:30:26,680 --> 00:30:27,680
Dad.

515
00:30:31,079 --> 00:30:32,079
Dad.

516
00:30:33,519 --> 00:30:34,519
Are you okay?

517
00:30:44,039 --> 00:30:45,519
He was with me for so many years.

518
00:30:50,559 --> 00:30:53,240
I never imagined it would be him.

519
00:30:55,039 --> 00:30:56,319
How is this possible?

520
00:30:58,599 --> 00:31:01,640
That old fox. How ungrateful.

521
00:31:02,759 --> 00:31:04,640
Not only did he transfer away my money,

522
00:31:05,200 --> 00:31:07,279
but he also hired someone to threaten you.

523
00:31:08,240 --> 00:31:10,319
I won't forgive him.

524
00:31:13,480 --> 00:31:15,359
From the sound of his voice,

525
00:31:17,359 --> 00:31:18,759
he seemed a bit weird just now.

526
00:31:20,440 --> 00:31:22,319
He wouldn't do anything foolish, would he?

527
00:31:22,720 --> 00:31:23,799
Do something foolish?

528
00:31:26,799 --> 00:31:28,880
If he commits suicide, that's letting him have it too easy.

529
00:31:30,440 --> 00:31:33,279
I have to make him tell me why he did this.

530
00:31:33,279 --> 00:31:34,279
Why?

531
00:31:39,640 --> 00:31:41,079
Okay, I understand. Thank you.

532
00:31:42,559 --> 00:31:43,559
Mr. Hou.

533
00:31:44,440 --> 00:31:45,440
Tian Min unfortunately died in a landslide...

534
00:31:45,440 --> 00:31:46,880
when she went to work as a volunteer teacher.

535
00:31:47,000 --> 00:31:48,200
She's buried at Nanshan Cemetery.

536
00:31:48,359 --> 00:31:49,839
I think that's where Ma Yong is right now.

537
00:31:54,640 --> 00:31:56,640
Is Tian Min involved in this?

538
00:31:56,960 --> 00:31:58,240
They were in a romantic relationship.

539
00:31:58,240 --> 00:31:59,240
They kept it a secret.

540
00:32:07,119 --> 00:32:08,519
I'll go there right now.

541
00:32:19,880 --> 00:32:20,880
Tian Min.

542
00:32:22,599 --> 00:32:24,079
I came to say goodbye.

543
00:32:27,119 --> 00:32:28,480
I might not be able to visit you...

544
00:32:28,480 --> 00:32:30,079
for a long time.

545
00:32:32,440 --> 00:32:34,079
The police came to the office today.

546
00:32:36,880 --> 00:32:38,559
But when I saw them,

547
00:32:39,160 --> 00:32:41,000
I actually felt relieved.

548
00:32:46,519 --> 00:32:47,640
You were right.

549
00:32:51,200 --> 00:32:52,880
Vengeance doesn't make people happy.

550
00:32:54,920 --> 00:32:56,079
Only love...

551
00:32:57,880 --> 00:32:59,799
will allow you to live in peace.

552
00:33:24,279 --> 00:33:26,480
(My love, Tian Min's grave)

553
00:33:27,799 --> 00:33:29,359
Why did you do this?

554
00:33:45,359 --> 00:33:48,400
Answer me. Why?

555
00:33:50,200 --> 00:33:51,359
It's because my last name is not Hou.

556
00:33:53,759 --> 00:33:55,640
Because in your eyes, I'll always be...

557
00:33:56,440 --> 00:33:57,799
an outsider with other intentions.

558
00:34:01,880 --> 00:34:03,039
I did it all by myself.

559
00:34:05,200 --> 00:34:08,159
Hiring Liu Tie Hao to threaten Hou Jue,

560
00:34:09,329 --> 00:34:12,159
hacking the Zhirong website, and taking 20 million from you...

561
00:34:12,159 --> 00:34:13,289
I did it all alone.

562
00:34:13,960 --> 00:34:15,599
You can do whatever you want to me. I'll accept it.

563
00:34:16,719 --> 00:34:17,719
Ma Yong.

564
00:34:19,000 --> 00:34:20,360
All these years,

565
00:34:21,809 --> 00:34:23,559
have I not been good enough to you?

566
00:34:23,679 --> 00:34:25,769
All these years, was I not loyal enough to you?

567
00:34:29,400 --> 00:34:31,440
I joined Zhirong Construction as soon as I graduated from college.

568
00:34:32,639 --> 00:34:34,000
I never changed my job.

569
00:34:35,719 --> 00:34:37,400
I thought of this company as my home.

570
00:34:38,289 --> 00:34:40,079
I regarded you as my older brother.

571
00:34:40,519 --> 00:34:42,809
I ran errands for you and served as your assistant.

572
00:34:44,079 --> 00:34:46,079
I respected you like you were my dad.

573
00:34:46,679 --> 00:34:48,559
I worked 13 years for you.

574
00:34:52,289 --> 00:34:54,679
I always remember you told me this many times.

575
00:34:56,920 --> 00:34:57,960
"Ma Yong."

576
00:34:59,769 --> 00:35:01,480
"One day, when I can't do this anymore,"

577
00:35:02,920 --> 00:35:04,199
"I'll let you..."

578
00:35:06,400 --> 00:35:07,559
"take over the company."

579
00:35:11,329 --> 00:35:13,440
I was so touched back then.

580
00:35:13,440 --> 00:35:14,679
I told myself...

581
00:35:14,679 --> 00:35:16,079
that I must repay you.

582
00:35:17,360 --> 00:35:19,000
That's why I always put your interests...

583
00:35:19,000 --> 00:35:20,519
and the company's interests first.

584
00:35:20,519 --> 00:35:22,769
I didn't care about money. I didn't want a high salary.

585
00:35:23,639 --> 00:35:24,840
I watched you...

586
00:35:25,119 --> 00:35:26,289
I watched you...

587
00:35:27,039 --> 00:35:28,809
use everyone around you...

588
00:35:28,809 --> 00:35:30,920
and break your promises to them,

589
00:35:30,920 --> 00:35:32,559
but I still insisted on believing...

590
00:35:32,559 --> 00:35:34,840
that your feelings and trust for me were different.

591
00:35:37,239 --> 00:35:38,360
Until...

592
00:35:39,039 --> 00:35:40,039
Mr. Hou,

593
00:35:40,480 --> 00:35:42,329
until the day you were taken hostage by Xiao Wei,

594
00:35:43,809 --> 00:35:45,239
I was outside your hospital room.

595
00:35:46,519 --> 00:35:48,519
I personally heard you tell Hou Jue.

596
00:35:51,079 --> 00:35:52,840
"This is a family business."

597
00:35:53,329 --> 00:35:54,719
"Ma Yong is very smart."

598
00:35:54,880 --> 00:35:56,880
"He works conscientiously and diligently."

599
00:35:56,880 --> 00:35:57,920
"But he's an outsider."

600
00:35:57,920 --> 00:35:58,920
"Outsiders may have other intentions."

601
00:35:58,920 --> 00:36:00,039
"We have to be careful of them."

602
00:36:02,199 --> 00:36:03,679
I worked hard for 13 years.

603
00:36:06,639 --> 00:36:08,079
I worked hard for 13 years,

604
00:36:08,079 --> 00:36:10,679
but all I got were these honest words from you.

605
00:36:10,679 --> 00:36:11,679
Mr. Hou.

606
00:36:14,920 --> 00:36:16,920
I'm just a lackey to you, aren't I?

607
00:36:17,400 --> 00:36:19,039
I'm just an employee who's a total bargain.

608
00:36:19,039 --> 00:36:20,960
You'll always be the boss, right?

609
00:36:21,880 --> 00:36:23,519
That's why I hired Liu Tie Hao.

610
00:36:24,440 --> 00:36:27,079
But I didn't plan on harming Hou Jue.

611
00:36:27,289 --> 00:36:28,679
I just wanted to create a fake scenario...

612
00:36:28,679 --> 00:36:29,679
to make him leave.

613
00:36:30,559 --> 00:36:32,000
But I didn't expect you to find her.

614
00:36:33,000 --> 00:36:34,809
She ruined all my plans.

615
00:36:40,159 --> 00:36:41,159
Fine.

616
00:36:41,289 --> 00:36:43,119
Since I can't get what I want,

617
00:36:43,119 --> 00:36:44,519
then I have to use my own way...

618
00:36:44,519 --> 00:36:46,809
to get all the value I lost over the past 13 years!

619
00:36:47,480 --> 00:36:49,840
Do you know you almost made the company go bankrupt?

620
00:36:49,840 --> 00:36:50,840
That wasn't my original intention.

621
00:36:50,840 --> 00:36:53,159
Didn't I return every single penny in the end?

622
00:36:54,159 --> 00:36:56,199
Then why did you transfer the money back?

623
00:37:00,719 --> 00:37:03,480
(My love, Tian Min's grave)

624
00:37:06,079 --> 00:37:07,079
Tian Min.

625
00:37:10,639 --> 00:37:13,519
Tian Min died...

626
00:37:14,360 --> 00:37:15,769
all because I wanted revenge on you.

627
00:37:19,480 --> 00:37:22,809
Tian Min urged me not to do it, but I didn't listen.

628
00:37:23,480 --> 00:37:25,769
But she still never left my side.

629
00:37:28,039 --> 00:37:29,519
But I took advantage of her love.

630
00:37:29,519 --> 00:37:31,719
I made her wait and bear with it.

631
00:37:31,719 --> 00:37:33,329
Until one day, she couldn't take it anymore.

632
00:37:33,329 --> 00:37:35,239
She ran away from home and was killed in an accident.

633
00:37:37,769 --> 00:37:38,769
That's when I realized...

634
00:37:42,440 --> 00:37:43,840
everything I was doing...

635
00:37:45,679 --> 00:37:47,159
was meaningless.

636
00:37:48,360 --> 00:37:49,809
It took me 13 years...

637
00:37:49,809 --> 00:37:51,559
and I ended up becoming like you.

638
00:38:00,400 --> 00:38:02,440
That's why I had to return the money to you.

639
00:38:02,769 --> 00:38:05,920
I don't know whether you're smart or stupid.

640
00:38:08,360 --> 00:38:12,360
When I found out that this was all your doing,

641
00:38:14,239 --> 00:38:16,039
do you know how I felt?

642
00:38:16,679 --> 00:38:18,400
Do you know how I felt?

643
00:38:22,079 --> 00:38:23,440
Do you know how hopeless I felt?

644
00:38:33,360 --> 00:38:37,559
Tian Min worked for me for many years.

645
00:38:39,239 --> 00:38:42,039
I don't really remember her that well.

646
00:38:43,400 --> 00:38:44,519
I only remember...

647
00:38:44,769 --> 00:38:49,329
she was good-tempered, kind, and hardworking.

648
00:38:50,559 --> 00:38:51,880
But I can't believe...

649
00:38:53,360 --> 00:38:56,880
she passed away at such a young age.

650
00:39:00,400 --> 00:39:02,880
I know the pain of losing one's family.

651
00:39:03,679 --> 00:39:05,239
I've been there.

652
00:39:05,639 --> 00:39:07,329
Only those who have experienced it...

653
00:39:07,480 --> 00:39:09,559
know how it feels.

654
00:39:11,199 --> 00:39:13,559
Tian Min traded her death...

655
00:39:13,920 --> 00:39:15,679
for your life.

656
00:39:16,880 --> 00:39:18,719
She wants the best for you.

657
00:39:19,960 --> 00:39:22,239
I've heard your confession.

658
00:39:27,289 --> 00:39:28,769
The repentance in your heart...

659
00:39:30,159 --> 00:39:33,119
is the best punishment for yourself.

660
00:39:40,480 --> 00:39:42,519
Today, I'll make a promise in front of Tian Min.

661
00:39:45,480 --> 00:39:46,809
I, Hou Zhi Rong,

662
00:39:49,679 --> 00:39:52,119
will not pursue...

663
00:39:56,159 --> 00:39:57,440
all the things you've done.

664
00:39:59,289 --> 00:40:00,480
From now on,

665
00:40:01,920 --> 00:40:03,000
I just hope...

666
00:40:03,679 --> 00:40:05,719
you can walk your own path properly.

667
00:40:06,519 --> 00:40:09,000
This is where we part.

668
00:40:10,289 --> 00:40:11,289
Thank you.

669
00:40:13,769 --> 00:40:14,769
Mr. Hou.

670
00:40:49,519 --> 00:40:52,920
(My love, Tian Min's grave)

671
00:41:23,920 --> 00:41:25,289
He did so many bad things.

672
00:41:26,809 --> 00:41:28,199
Are you forgiving him just like that?

673
00:41:31,920 --> 00:41:33,809
Zhirong Construction is where it is today...

674
00:41:34,519 --> 00:41:35,719
thanks to his contributions.

675
00:41:36,719 --> 00:41:39,199
But I never knew what he was thinking...

676
00:41:39,920 --> 00:41:41,159
nor did I want to know.